System Integrations
--------------------------------
Clipboard
Drag and Drop
Open File
Trash File
Browse URI
Mailto URI
Application Menu
Print Document
System Tray
System Notifications
File Chooser Dialog
Folder Chooser Dialog
Font Chooser Dialog
Color Picker Dialog
Message Box Dialog
Question Box Dialog
Input Box Dialog
Password Box Dialog
System Preferences [Windows Registry, macOS/iOS NSUserDefaults, UNIX INI configuration file]
Joystick [Windows DirectInput/XInput, macOS/iOS Game Controller Framework, Linux/FreeBSD <linux/joystick.h>, UNIX SDL_Joystick]
JavaScript Engine [macOS/iOS JavaScriptCore (JIT disabled), other QuickJS]
--------------------------------

--------------------------------
Networking
--------------------------------
TCP/UDP/SSL Socket
HTTP/HTTPS
WebSocket
Networking [Single-instance factory]
--------------------------------

--------------------------------
Console/Terminal
--------------------------------
ANSI Escape Code [Windows require extra work, other platforms natively supported]
REPL Console
Curses
--------------------------------

--------------------------------
Data Serialization/Deserialization
--------------------------------
JSON [Desktop modified org.json, Android/RoboVM SDK JSON API, TeaVM HTML5 JSON API]
XML DOM SAX XPath [Desktop javax.xml, Android/RoboVM SDK XML API, TeaVM HTML5 XML API]
INI
Properties
Binary [Bit-based I/O as enhancement required]
--------------------------------

--------------------------------
Embedded Native Widgets
--------------------------------
Video Player [Windows Media Player Control, macOS/iOS AVPlayer, UNIX GStreamer, Android VideoView]
WebView [Windows WebView2, macOS/iOS WKWebView, UNIX WebKitGTK, Android WebView]
--------------------------------

--------------------------------
Music/Sound Effects
--------------------------------
Music [Long, streaming-playing music]
Sound [Short, memory-buffered sound effects]
AudioTrack [Directly read pcm from microphone or write pcm to speaker]
Sampled [Single-instance factory, create audio instances, decoder/encoder for several audio formats]
--------------------------------

